rule.description:
Use the SonarQube MCP server with credentials from environment variables:

MCP Server Configuration:
- Server Name: sonarqube
- URL: ${SONARQUBE_MCP_URL}
- Transport: SSE

Authentication:
- Token: ${SONARQUBE_TOKEN}
- Base URL: ${SONARQUBE_BASE_URL}
- Note: Credentials are loaded from .env file via environment variables

UI Access (for reference):
- URL: ${SONARQUBE_BASE_URL}/sessions/new
- Username: ${SONARQUBE_USERNAME}
- Password: ${SONARQUBE_PASSWORD}
